0.03    2019-02-19 15:16:11
        [CHANGES]
         * Updates to latest inc/Alien/make/Module/Build.pm
            + Don't bother with -Wl,-rpath hackery because
              Module::Build::Using::PkgConfig should handle it instead
            + Defer mangling of paths in .pc file until ACTION_install time,
              thus allowing never-installed `cpan> test` dependency trees
              to work

0.02    2019-02-17 13:23:19
        [CHANGES]
         * Updates to latest inc/Alien/make/Module/Build.pm
            + Don't bother with two-stage rewrite of .pc file; do it in one
              step
         * Use libtickit 0.2a
            + Makefile fixes for unit tests against non-system installed
              unibilium or libtermkey
            + Don't install empty manpage links

0.01    2019-02-17 01:49:56
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

